{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/open-mysql-binlog-for-mac/","webpackCompilationHash":"1455429ce6c1c2296cb9","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Nocoder Blog","author":"Jason Yang"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4073aed0-0b2c-5e6f-917a-5ad4673b5340","excerpt":"MySQL for Mac 默认 bin log 是关闭的，使用以下命令查看 bin log 是否开启： Variable_name Value log_bin OFF 修改/etc/my.conf，没有文件就新建一个，添加以下配置： 重启MySQL，再次查看 bin log 状态： Variable_name Value log_bin ON","html":"<p>MySQL for Mac 默认 bin log 是关闭的，使用以下命令查看 bin log 是否开启：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">SHOW</span> VARIABLES <span class=\"token operator\">LIKE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'log_bin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Variable_name</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>log_bin</td>\n<td>OFF</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>修改/etc/my.conf，没有<code class=\"language-text\">my.conf</code>文件就新建一个，添加以下配置：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>mysqld<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nlog-bin<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>mysql-bin <span class=\"token comment\">#添加这一行就ok</span>\nbinlog-format<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>ROW <span class=\"token comment\">#选择row模式</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">server_id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#配置mysql replaction需要定义，不能和canal的slaveId重复</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>重启MySQL<code class=\"language-text\">系统偏好设置-&gt;MySQL-&gt;Stop MySQL Server -&gt; Start MySQL Server</code>，再次查看 bin log 状态：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">SHOW</span> VARIABLES <span class=\"token operator\">LIKE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'log_bin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Variable_name</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>log_bin</td>\n<td>ON</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","frontmatter":{"title":"Mac 下 MySQL 开启 bin log","date":"2018-07-23"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/open-mysql-binlog-for-mac/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/docker-practice-notes/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Docker Practice Notes 01"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/ssh-proxy/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"开启ssh代理服务"}}}}}